meta {
  name: Get User Tag Games
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/users/:username/tags/:tagName/games?page=0&size=20&sort=updatedAt,desc
  body: none
  auth: none
}

params:path {
  username: gamer123
  tagName: cozy
}

query {
  page: 0
  size: 20
  sort: updatedAt,desc
}

docs {
  # Get User Tag Games (Public)

  Returns paginated play logs for a user's tag, identified by username and tag name.
  This is a public endpoint — no authentication required.

  ## Path Parameters

  - **username**: The user's display name (pseudo)
  - **tagName**: The tag name (case-insensitive, will be normalized)

  ## Query Parameters

  | Parameter | Default | Description |
  |-----------|---------|-------------|
  | page | 0 | Page number (0-based) |
  | size | 20 | Page size (max 100) |
  | sort | updatedAt,desc | Sort field and direction |

  ## Response (200 OK)

  Returns a paginated response with play log entries.

  ## Error Responses

  - **404 Not Found**: User or tag does not exist
}
